Knockout tokenInput binding and forked jquery-tokeninput plugin
=======================================================

Overview
--------
This is forked version of jquery-tokeninput plugin with some changes that allowed me to make KO custom binding for it.

Documentation, Features and Demos
---------------------------------
See usage example on <http://jsfiddle.net/vittore/8jjWW/2/>
tagline: Forked tokenInput from http://loopj.com/jquery-tokeninput/ with added knockout.js binding
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
name: Jquery-tokeninput
